FT  16 OCT 93 / Coal safeguard
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE GOVERNMENT said yesterday that it would safeguard concessionary fuel
entitlements of British Coal employees following privatisation. In a
consultation document the Department of Trade and Industry said the fuel
obligations towards former employees would be transferred from British Coal
to the secretary of state after privatisation.
