<HEADLINE>
FT  15 OCT 93 / People: Non-executive directors - Waterman Partnership
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
William Mathieson, a former director of Land Securities, at WATERMAN
PARTNERSHIP.
</TEXT>
<XX>
