5 per cent to Dollars 2.22bn, from Dollars 2.35bn a year earlier.
Excluding special factors, however, the decline in earnings was marginal.
The 1993 results included a charge of 10 cents a share to provide for
changes in the federal corporate tax rate enacted this summer.
Last year's figure, meanwhile, reflected a one-time gain of 8 cents a share
